<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background:inherit; font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">Malazan Book of the Fallen <span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Malazan+Book+of+the+Fallen&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BSteven+Erikson%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B1+April%5D%5D+%5B%5B1999%5D%5D+-+Ongoing&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BBantam+Books%5D%5D&amp;rft.pages=6974+%28U.K.%3B+total+pgs+of+first+7+books%29">&#160;</span></td>
</tr>
