<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/pe.cgi?Malazan_Book_of_the_Fallen" class="external text" title="http://www.isfdb.org/cgi-bin/pe.cgi?Malazan_Book_of_the_Fallen" rel="nofollow">Malazan Book of the Fallen</a> series listing at the <a href="/wiki/Internet_Speculative_Fiction_Database" title="Internet Speculative Fiction Database" class="mw-redirect">Internet Speculative Fiction Database</a></li>
