<li><a href="http://encyclopediamalazica.pbwiki.com/" class="external text" title="http://encyclopediamalazica.pbwiki.com/" rel="nofollow">Encyclopaedia Malazica</a> - Major wiki, frequented by Steven Erikson.</li>
